The reason: existing nuclear has been left out. In this episode, we'll talk with energy analyst Jesse Jenkins about why maintaining nuclear plants is vital to keeping Obama's climate rule from collapsing. 

Later in the show, we'll talk about the fight over demand response that hit the Supreme Court this week. We'll also look at how energy and climate were discussed during the Democratic presidential debate.&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/TheEnergyGang/~4/AZNf0Ee-V8c" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
      
