      <title>Is Nuclear 2.0 Possible?</title>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2015 20:05:42 +0000</pubDate>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TheEnergyGang/~3/zDnfU3AvUR8/is-nuclear-20-possible</link>
